docs.text: Pypi-M-1 [ ][conventional commits] [docs-url]: A general template that helps you jump start your project Documentation: [][docs-url] GitHub: https://github.com/MoonJaehyun/pypi-M-1 PyPI: https://pypi.org/project/Pypi-M-1 Hyperfast Template is a self-contained template that helps you initialize your project inside the template. It is hyperfast in the sense that the template itself is converted into a project in the blink of an eye. It is also hyperfast in the sense that it helps you jump start your project with the best practices in the dev community. Changelog See the CHANGELOG for more information.
